Inertia Revision History

4/11/98---------------------------------------------------------------------
  Version 1.10

  - Added Windows support via MSVC++ v5.0

4/8/98----------------------------------------------------------------------
  Version 1.02

  - Fixed perspective texture mapping bug in Watcom C version of Inertia that
    involved clipped polygons on the left side of the screen.

  - Dropped support for Inertia/16 (If you really want Inertia/16, I can
    get a version of it to you).


12/23/97--------------------------------------------------------------------
  Version 1.01

  - Added 3dfx Glide rasterization to Watcom C version of Inertia/32

10/4/97--------------------------------------------------------------------
  Version 1.0

  Major overhaul to Inertia.
    - Added support for TMT Pascal and Watcom C (both 32-bit).
    - Updated 16-bit version with smaller code size and newer API.
    - Opal program is now STab (shade table).
    - Documentation in MS Word.

2/30/96--------------------------------------------------------------------
  Version 0.99

  - GVO Converter re-write. Cleared some confusion with old version numbers.

11/20/96-------------------------------------------------------------------
  Version 0.90

  - Initial Inertia Release
